    "body": "The current blend modes are ad-hoc, and don't follow a consistent design.  At a minimum I expect we will want to rename the `Translucency` blend mode.  I strongly suspect that the proper fix will be to remove the sequence `Alpha`, and implement proper pre-multiplied alpha options on the palettes themselves.\n"
